    "body":  "The current subtitle under the “Upload Qualifications” header reads: “Upload your CV or training certificates to automatically extract qualifications.”\n\nThis line gives clear functional instruction, but it doesn’t explain the value of the action to the user. Adding a brief benefit-oriented tagline will reinforce why the user should engage.\n\n**Requested Change**\nAdd the following sentence directly beneath the current subtitle: “Save time, reduce manual entry, and keep your qualifications profile audit-ready.”\n\nUI Placement\n- Below the existing instructional line\n- Same font style (smaller than header)\n- If possible, slightly muted (e.g., gray text) to differentiate tone from the main instruction\n\nGoal\nMake the value of uploading documents immediately clear and compelling to first-time users or viewers.",
